- cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory) is a possible category because the paper is about improving a game-solving algorithm. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is possible because the paper discusses the theoretical convergence rate of an algorithm and proposes a new variant. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is less likely but still possible because the paper discusses stability and predictivity of the algorithm, which are concepts relevant to control systems.
